org.csstudio.alarm.jms2ora.database
Class MessageTypeTObject

java.lang.Object
  org.csstudio.alarm.jms2ora.database.MessageTypeTObject

public class MessageTypeTObject
extends java.lang.Object

The class MessageTypeTObject is a representation of a message type. It contains the type and the properties of a message that is stored in the alarm database.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Markus Moeller
